<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Vege產品資訊</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/img/fruitbox_s.png" />
    <%- include('share/head_link') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/Product_Page.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/loadingio/loading.css@v2.0.0/dist/loading.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="black"></div>
    <%- include('share/header') %> <%- include('share/modal') %>
    <header>
      <main id="product_main">
        <section class="main-box">
          <section class="middleContent d-flex">
            <aside class="asideNav fu_tab">
              <ul class="asideNav-ul" id="parentElement">
                <% for (let i = 0; i < data.names.length; i++) { %>
                <li class="vg-bd-5">
                  <button
                    class="tab btn mt-4 vg-p act"
                    onclick="openCity(event, 'fu_tab<%= i+1 %>')"
                  >
                    <%= data.names[i].product %>
                  </button>
                </li>
                <% } %>
              </ul>
            </aside>
            <% for(let t = 0 ; t < data.names.length ; t++){ %>
            <section id="fu_tab<%= t+1 %>" class="flex-column middle_box1">
              <div class="middle_box mt-3">
                <div class="vg-h3 vg-h3-div">
                  <h3 class="vg-h3"><%= data.con[t].product %></h3>
                </div>
                <div class="vg-h3-div2 fu_Mnav">
                  <div class="box">
                    <button class="btn fu_nav vg-p">菜單特色</button>
                  </div>
                  <!-- <div class="box">
                    <button class="btn fu_nav vg-p">週週訂閱</button>
                  </div> -->
                  <div class="box">
                    <button class="btn fu_nav vg-p">購買須知</button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="box">
                    <button class="btn fu_nav vg-p">最新活動</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="middle_all">
                <div class="middle_img">
                  <img class="mainImg" src="<%= data.con[t].image %>" />
                  <!-- 取得這個img當作購物圖片-->
                  <div class="middle_imgs">
                    <% for(let i = 0; i < data.images.length; i++) { %>
                    <img class="ch" src="<%= data.images[i].image %>" />
                    <% } %>
                  </div>
                  <div class="smtext">
                    <h5 class="vg-h4">貼心小叮嚀</h5>

                    <p class="vg-h5">
                      蔬果:<span class="vg-p ms-2 productInfo"></span>
                    </p>
                    <p class="vg-h5">
                      產地:<span class="vg-p ms-2 productOrigin"></span>
                    </p>
                    <p class="vg-h5">
                      保存方法:<span class="vg-p ms-2 saveInfo"></span>
                    </p>
                    <p class="vg-h5">
                      注意事項:<span class="vg-p ms-2 noteInfo"></span>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% if(data.con[t].product === data.con[6].product) { %>
                <div class="middle_Con">
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">菜單特色:</h5>
                  <p class="vg-p"><%= data.con[t].feature %></p>

                  <h5 class="vg-h5">蔬果內容:</h5>
                  <div class="div_2">
                    <p class="vg-p p-0 m-0">每箱 <%= data.con[t].content %></p>
                  </div>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">運送頻率:</h5>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    基本每周一次 ➞ 一期四箱
                    <br />
                    訂購期 30 天 <br />(需於45天內配送完畢&含延後2次)
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    訂購期 60 天 <br />(需於90天內配送完畢 &含延後2次)
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">購買單箱1~5個工作天配送完畢</p>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">商品價格:</h5>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    <span>單箱最低金額:</span
                    ><span class="price1"> <%= data.con[t].price %></span>元
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    <span>單箱最高金額:</span>
                    <span class="price3"
                      ><%= parseInt(data.con[t].price)+200 %></span
                    >元
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    雙人箱:<span class="sp2">一期運費160元</span>
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    家庭箱:<span class="sp2">一期運費290元</span>
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">
                    選擇商品規格:
                    <br />
                    <span class="text-danger vg-p">
                      訂閱一期享有運費優惠！
                    </span>
                  </h5>
                  <div class="fv_all">
                    <div class="fv_con">
                      <label for="commodity" class="vg-p">選擇商品:</label>
                      <select class="commodity vg-p">
                        <option></option>
                        <option value="once" data-size="s">
                          雙人箱(1~2人)
                        </option>
                        <option value="once" data-size="l">
                          家庭箱(3~4人)
                        </option>
                        <option value="30d" data-size="s">雙人箱(30day)</option>
                        <option value="60d" data-size="l">雙人箱(60day)</option>
                        <option value="30d" data-size="s">家庭箱(30day)</option>
                        <option value="60d" data-size="l">家庭箱(60day)</option>
                      </select>
                      <p class="p-0 m-0 vg-p dis">
                        單箱金額: <span class="toal price4">0</span>元
                      </p>
                      <div class="vg-p fm">
                        家庭箱金額:<span class="price6">0</span>元
                      </div>
                      <div class="day">
                        <p class="p-0 m-0 vg-p">
                          總金額: <span class="price5">0</span>元
                        </p>
                        <label for="commodity" class="vg-p">配送日:</label>
                        <select class="commodity vg-p">
                          <option value="" selected></option>
                          <option value="Monday">星期一</option>
                          <option value="Wednesday">星期三</option>
                        </select>
                      </div>
                      <span class="d-inline vg-p">數量:</span>
                      <span
                        class="fa-solid fa-plus btn price1"
                        style="font-size: 20px"
                      ></span>
                      <span class="sum">1</span>
                      <span
                        class="fa-solid fa-minus btn price3"
                        style="font-size: 20px"
                      ></span>
                      <div class="fv_box vg-bd-5">
                        <div class="vg-bd-5 mo_con">
                          <div
                            class="mo_header vg-bd-5 d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center"
                          >
                            <h4 class="vg-h4 mb-0">請選擇您喜歡的蔬果</h4>
                            <strong class="over"></strong>
                            <button
                              type="button"
                              class="btn-close bcl"
                            ></button>
                          </div>
                          <div class="cons">
                            <h5 class="vg-h5"><strong>蔬菜</strong></h5>
                            <% for(let f = 0 ;f < data.veg.length ;f++ ){ %>
                            <button class="btn f_1 f_2 vg-p" data-pay="100">
                              <%= data.veg[f].product %>
                            </button>
                            <% } %>
                            <h5 class="vg-h5 hoh5"><strong>水果</strong></h5>
                            <% for(let f = 0 ;f < data.fruit.length ;f++ ){ %>
                            <button class="btn f_1 f_2 vg-p" data-pay="50">
                              <%= data.fruit[f].product %>
                            </button>
                            <% } %>
                          </div>
                          <div
                            class="mo_foot vg-p d-flex justify-content-end align-items-center"
                          >
                            <span>圖標:</span>
                            <span
                              ><img src="/img/天平.png" class="bas" />平性</span
                            >
                            <span>
                              <i
                                class="fa-solid fa-fire dd"
                                style="color: #ff0000"
                              ></i>
                              熱性</span
                            >
                            <span
                              ><i
                                class="fa-solid fa-snowflake dd"
                                style="color: rgb(142, 169, 215)"
                              ></i
                              >寒性</span
                            >
                            <button class="btn btn-vg goSure">確認</button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <br />
                      <p class="d-inline vg-p">內容:</p>
                      <strong class="buyfv buyfv2 vg-p"></strong>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-vg chage ms-1 mt-3">選擇蔬果</button>
                    <button class="addCard btn btn-vg mt-3">加入購物車</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% } else { %>
                <div class="middle_Con">
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">菜單特色:</h5>
                  <p class="vg-p"><%= data.con[t].feature %></p>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">蔬果內容:</h5>
                  <div class="div_2 vg-p">
                    <p class="m-0">
                      <span class="sp1">雙人箱:</span>
                      <span class="concon"><%= data.con[t].content %></span>
                    </p>
                    <p class="m-0">
                      <span class="sp1">家庭箱:</span>
                      <% if(data.con[t].product === data.con[2].product){ %>
                      <span class="concon2">八樣水果</span>
                      <% }else if(data.con[t].product === data.con[3].product){
                      %>
                      <span class="concon2">十樣蔬菜</span>
                      <% }else{ %>
                      <span class="concon2">五樣水果、五樣蔬菜</span>
                      <% }%>
                    </p>
                    <span class="vg-p">(內容以當季蔬菜組裝出貨)</span>
                  </div>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">運送頻率:</h5>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    每周一次 ➞ 一期四箱
                    <br />
                    訂購期 30 天 <br />
                    (需於45天內配送完畢&含延後2次)
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    訂購期 60 天<br />
                    (需於90天內配送完畢 &含延後2次)
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">購買單箱1~5個工作天配送完畢</p>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">商品價格:</h5>

                  <p class="vg-p">
                    <span>雙人箱(1~2人)</span
                    ><span class="price1"> <%= data.con[t].price %></span>元
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    <span>家庭箱(3~4人)</span>
                    <span class="price3"
                      ><%= parseInt(data.con[t].price)+200 %></span
                    >元
                  </p>
                  <p class="vg-p">
                    運費根據黑貓低溫配送基本價 <br />
                    宅配/超商取貨為同樣價格
                  </p>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">
                    選擇商品規格:
                    <br />
                    <span class="text-danger vg-p">
                      訂閱一期享有運費優惠！
                    </span>
                  </h5>

                  <label for="commodity" class="mt-2 vg-p">選擇商品:</label>
                  <select class="commodity vg-p">
                    <option></option>
                    <option value="once" data-size="s">雙人箱(1~2人)</option>
                    <option value="once" data-size="l">家庭箱(3~4人)</option>
                    <option value="30d" data-size="s">雙人箱(30day)</option>
                    <option value="60d" data-size="l">雙人箱(60day)</option>
                    <option value="30d" data-size="s">家庭箱(30day)</option>
                    <option value="60d" data-size="l">家庭箱(60day)</option>
                  </select>
                  <br />
                  <div class="day">
                    <label for="commodity" class="vg-p">配送日:</label>
                    <select class="commodity vg-p">
                      <option selected></option>
                      <option value="Monday">星期一</option>
                      <option value="Wednesday">星期三</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <br />
                  <span class="d-inline vg-p">數量:</span>
                  <span
                    class="fa-solid fa-plus btn price1"
                    style="font-size: 20px"
                  ></span>
                  <span class="sum">1</span>
                  <span
                    class="fa-solid fa-minus btn price3"
                    style="font-size: 20px"
                  ></span>
                  <button class="addCard btn btn-vg m-0">加入購物車</button>
                </div>
                <% } %>
                <div class="middle_Con">
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">
                    購買流程: <br />
                    <span class="text-danger vg-p"
                      >每周一固定配送 (假日無物流)</span
                    >
                  </h5>
                  <ol class="vg-p">
                    <li>選購產品</li>
                    <li>選擇規格(份量/運送方式/頻率)</li>
                    <li>下訂(客製需求/訂單備註/訂單資料)</li>
                    <li>付款</li>
                    <li>收貨</li>
                    <li>訂單回饋(獲得購物金)</li>
                  </ol>

                  <h5 class="vg-h5">
                    售後服務: <br />
                    <span class="text-danger vg-p"
                      >每筆訂單提供兩次延後配送的服務</span
                    >
                  </h5>

                  <ul class="vg-p">
                    <li>吃不完：訂購的蔬果多於您能在食用期限內消耗的量。</li>
                    <li>
                      臨時出國： 訂購後突然需要出國，無法在期限內食用所有蔬果。
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      臨時獲得蔬果：
                      在訂購後意外獲得其他新鮮蔬果，使您難以消耗所有訂購的蔬果。
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">客戶回報系統:</h5>
                  <ul class="vg-p">
                    <li>品項不好、有蟲、蔬果腐爛</li>
                    <li>拍照上傳客服</li>
                    <li>
                      我們將
                      <a
                        href="http://127.0.0.1:2407/contact/"
                        style="color: #1ebd95"
                      >
                        專人 </a
                      >為您服務
                    </li>
                  </ul>

                  <p class="vg-p">蔬菜內容以當季蔬菜組裝出貨！</p>
                </div>
                <div class="middle_Con">
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">最新活動</h5>
                  <p class="vg-p"><%= data.con[t].off_act %></p>
                  <h5 class="vg-h5">活動內容</h5>
                  <ul class="vg-p">
                    <li><%= data.con[t].act_content %></li>
                    <li><%= data.con[t].act_content2 %></li>
                    <li><%= data.con[t].act_content3 %></li>
                    <li><%= data.con[t].act_content4 %></li>
                    <li><%= data.con[t].act_content5 %></li>
                    <li><%= data.con[t].act_content6 %></li>
                  </ul>

                  <h5 class="vg-h5">活動時間</h5>
                  <h6>
                    <a
                      class="vg-p aa"
                      href="http://127.0.0.1:2407/activityboard/inside/2"
                      >點我看詳細活動</a
                    >
                  </h6>
                  <p class="vg-p"><%= data.con[t].act_time %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
            <% } %>
          </section>
        </section>
      </main>
    </header>
    <%- include('share/footer') %>
    <script src="js/vg.js"></script>
    <script src="js/Product_Page.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
